Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:09.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's over now, I kno-ow inside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:15.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No one will never know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:21.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sorry tale of Nightmare Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And those who died
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No one must ever know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:37.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They only see the tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:42.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They not see my intent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The shadow of Night's evil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:57.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Will forever kill the good that I have meant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:05.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Am I~ a go-ood mare?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Am I~ a ma-ad mare?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's such a fi-ine line~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:24.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Betwe-een a good ma-are a-and I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:36.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you even think that I would ever let you go~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:41.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you even think that I would set you free-ee?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:48.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'm sad to say it simply isn't so
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:54.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You will never get away fro-om me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that you are is a face in a mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I close my eyes and you disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm what you face when you face in the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Long as you live I will still be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that you are is the end of a Nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:13.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that you are is a dying scream~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:19.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After tonight I shall end these demon dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:24.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This is not a dream, my dear, and it will never e-end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:30.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This one is the nightmare that goes~ on~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:36.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I am here to stay, no matter what you may pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll flourish long after yo-ou're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Soon you will die and my silence will hide you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You cannot choose but to lose control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can't control me, I live deep inside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Each day you feel me devour your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to survive as you need me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll become whole, lest you dance with death
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:07.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll rejoice as you breathe your fina-al breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I~ live insi-ide yo-ou forever~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:12.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:17.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The darkness, itself by my si-ide
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:23.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll kno-ow that now a-and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:30.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They'll never be able to sepa-arate Luna from Night~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it's:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Over now~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, not I~, only yo-ou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If I die, you die too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You die. Me? I'll BE you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:49.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Damn you Night! Set me free!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can't you see? You ARE me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No! Deep insideâ€¦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I am you. You are Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes. Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,God damn you Nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Take all your evil deeds and run to Tartarus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Muhuhahahahahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll see you there, Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Mmhmmmhmmhmmhmmhmm waahaaha hahahahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, ha ha ha ha ha ha!